message: Let's get started! I'll give you a good deal, but don't expect me to go easy on you.
You're starting strong, but I'm not afraid to be ruthless. Time to make a move!
You think you're being ruthless? I'm just getting started!
You think you can outmaneuver me? Let's see how you like it!
You're trying to squeeze me, but I'm not going down without a fight!
You're not going down without a fight? I'm just getting started!
You're running out of time, Bob. Make a move or get left behind!
You're getting desperate, Alice. I'm not afraid to take the lead!
Desperate? Me? Never! I'm just getting creative!
You think you can outmaneuver me, Bob? Bring it on!
You're not getting any younger, Alice. Time to make a deal!
Age is just a number, Bob! And I'm not going to let you take advantage of me!
You're running out of time, Bob. Don't make me make the final move!
You're not getting the better deal, Alice. This is my last chance to take the lead!
You're grasping at straws, Bob! I'm not going to let you snatch victory from the jaws of defeat!
You're out of time, Bob. This is my final offer. Take it or leave it!
No more games, Alice. This is my final offer. Take it or we both walk away with nothing!
You're too late, Bob. I'd rather walk away with nothing than take a pittance like that!
